15. Quality Gates (Structural, Not Aspirational)

Every publish triggers:

1. WCAG AA — axe-core + Pa11y automated scan
2. Contrast Ratio — all text/background combinations checked
3. Core Web Vitals — Lighthouse CI performance budget
4. Security — CSP header validation, OWASP ZAP scan, no unapproved third-party scripts
5. Visual Regression — Chromatic/BackstopJS comparison against brand baseline
6. Token Compliance — No raw values outside the design token system

Failed gates block deployment. No override without platform-team approval.

