### Phase 4 — Legacy Decommissioning
**Months 18–30 | Old System Retired**

#### Key Shift
Legacy becomes read-only → removed. Platform operates entirely on new architecture.

#### Activities

**Remaining Page Migration**
- Auto-convert remaining legacy pages where pattern matching is high-confidence
