**AI-Driven A/B Testing**
- Platform autonomously proposes layout experiments based on analytics signals
- AI generates variant layouts (within design system bounds)
- A/B tests them; surfaces winners for editor approval

**Federated Governance Finalized**
- Central platform team: token foundation, registry, CI/CD, security
- Regional teams: token overlays, regional variants, first-line support
- Site teams: full self-service within scope
- RFC process for platform evolution: any team can propose changes; AI assists evaluation

